dotfiles
========

Setup

    git clone --recurse-submodules -j8 https://github.com/aca/dotfiles ~/src/configs/dotfiles
    bash ~/src/configs/dotfiles/.bin/setup.stow

Fix submodules 

    git submodule update --force --recursive --init --remote

Neovim
    sudo apt-get install ninja-build gettext libtool libtool-bin autoconf automake cmake g++ pkg-config unzip curl
    make distclean
    make -j4
    sudo make install

